{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.000", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.640", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Werte Abgeordnete! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.000", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Haushalt des Bundesministeriums f\u00fcr Ern\u00e4hrung und Landwirtschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.800", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kurz: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.680", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "BMEL, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.800", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "findet vor allem in der \u00d6ffentlichkeitsarbeit und der Forschung ein massiver, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.880", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "explosionsartiger Anstieg der Ausgaben statt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.680", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auf den ersten Blick scheinen die geplanten Ausgaben des BMEL f\u00fcr \u00d6ffentlichkeitsarbeit mit einem Haushaltssoll in 2018 in H\u00f6he von \u00fcber 1\u00a0Million Euro nicht allzu hoch zu sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.480", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn man es jedoch genau betrachtet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.280", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "stellt man fest: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.520", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das BMEL hat im Bereich der \u00d6ffentlichkeitsarbeit eine Spitzenstellung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.120", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ber\u00fccksichtigt man n\u00e4mlich alle Haushaltstitel des BMEL, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.720", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die werbewirksame Ma\u00dfnahmen betreffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.240", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Informationen f\u00fcr Verbraucher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.960", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Messen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.560", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ausstellungen und Fachinformationen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.600", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "summieren sich diese auf mehr als 50\u00a0Millionen Euro und damit auf mehr als bei den meisten anderen Ministerien."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.840", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Forschungsbereich findet an 17 verschiedenen Stellen des Einzelplans eine F\u00f6rderung mit Ausgabensteigerungen um teilweise 500 bis 1\u00a0300\u00a0Prozent im Vergleich zu 2016 statt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.840", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei hat das BMEL keine zus\u00e4tzlichen Aufgaben \u00fcbernommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.200", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Gegenteil: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.840", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Verbraucherpolitik wurde im Jahre\u00a02013 an das Justizministerium abgegeben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.080", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Aufgabenbereich damit also kleiner. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.480", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dennoch besteht beim BMEL ein ineffizientes und hochgradig intransparentes Geflecht von externen Forschungsauftr\u00e4gen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.240", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ministeriumseigenen Bundesforschungsinstituten und zus\u00e4tzlichen institutionell gef\u00f6rderten Forschungseinrichtungen au\u00dferhalb der Bundesverwaltung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.000", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor allem die ministeriumseigenen Bundesforschungsinstitute haben kr\u00e4ftige Ausgabensteigerungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.840", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So verzeichnet zum Beispiel das Bundesinstitut f\u00fcr Risikobewertung neben einer Kostensteigerung von 80\u00a0Prozent f\u00fcr \u00d6ffentlichkeitsarbeit von 2016 bis 2018 im selben Zeitraum eine Ausgabensteigerung von 55\u00a0Prozent bei den Beamten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.240", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Bundesinstitut f\u00fcr Risikobewertung ist nur ein Beispiel f\u00fcr die Ma\u00dflosigkeit der Ausgabensteigerung bei den bundeseigenen Forschungsinstituten; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.680", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn bei den anderen verh\u00e4lt es sich genauso."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.680", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Obwohl das BMEL mit seinen eigenen Forschungsinstituten \u00fcber eine \u00e4u\u00dferst gro\u00dfz\u00fcgige Ausstattung f\u00fcr Forschung verf\u00fcgt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.920", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unterst\u00fctzt es dar\u00fcber hinaus au\u00dferhalb der Bundesverwaltung zus\u00e4tzliche Forschungseinrichtungen mitsamt ihren kompletten Institutionen mit zig Millionen Euro."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.200", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Besonders die massiven Ausgabensteigerungen beim Bundesamt f\u00fcr Verbraucherschutz und Lebensmittelsicherheit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.400", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einer selbstst\u00e4ndigen Bundesoberbeh\u00f6rde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.080", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "fallen insoweit auf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.960", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch hier steigen die Ausgaben f\u00fcr Beamte von 2016 bis 2018 um fast 70 \u00a0Prozent, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.160", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und f\u00fcr IT und bei sogenannten vermischten Verwaltungsaufgaben verdreifachen sie sich sogar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.840", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch hier steht diese Institution nur als Beispiel f\u00fcr die anderen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.920", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine weitere Aufz\u00e4hlung erspare ich mir; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.800", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn ich denke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.840", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie alle haben verstanden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.840", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was hier passiert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.440", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und als wenn das alles nicht genug w\u00e4re, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.200", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "leistet sich das BMEL dar\u00fcber hinaus teure Forschungsprogramme, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.800", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "deren Sinn und Umsetzung zumindest zweifelhaft sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.480", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein Paradebeispiel hierf\u00fcr ist das Bundesprogramm \u201eL\u00e4ndliche Entwicklung\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.520", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Jahre\u00a02018 mit einem Plansoll von 55\u00a0Millionen Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.880", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Abgesehen davon, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.760", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass hier schon fraglich ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.960", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob der Bund \u00fcberhaupt berechtigt ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.880", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an dieser Stelle auf die Kofinanzierung der L\u00e4nder zu verzichten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.280", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wozu er bei Aufgaben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.560", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die direkt in Landeszust\u00e4ndigkeiten eingreifen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.560", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nach dem Grundgesetz generell verpflichtet ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.680", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat ein Modul dieses Bundesprogramms den sch\u00f6nen Namen \u201eLandaufschwung\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.520", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wovon sich das BMEL neue Impulse f\u00fcr das Leben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.080", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Arbeiten und Miteinander in l\u00e4ndlichen Regionen verspricht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.520", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Praktisch gibt es hier f\u00fcr junge Sauerl\u00e4nder nach den Recherchen des Bundes der Steuerzahler die \u201eHEIMVORTEIL2Go\u201c-Box, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.680", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Produkte aus der Heimat enthalten soll. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.520", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Laut Initiative befinden sich darin unter anderem eine Luftpumpe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.960", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein USB-Stick sowie eine Dose Bier einer regionalen Brauerei, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.480", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und in Sachsen werden davon unter anderem Kaninchenst\u00e4lle f\u00fcr den \u00f6rtlichen Kaninchenz\u00fcchterverein sowie die Instandsetzung eines historischen Traktors finanziert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.440", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit dem Steuergeld sollen passgenaue Zukunftskonzepte vorangebracht werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "287.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.120", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie das BMEL hierzu auf Nachfrage des Bundes der Steuerzahler mitgeteilt hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "295.680", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wo aber ist hier das Zukunftskonzept?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "295.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "308.480", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Art F\u00f6rderung von 13\u00a0Modellregionen zuz\u00fcglich dreier Sonderprojekte und einer Begleitforschung kostet uns Steuerzahler insgesamt rund 31\u00a0Millionen Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "308.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "312.880", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Urspr\u00fcnglich sollte diese F\u00f6rderung Mitte\u00a02018 auslaufen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "312.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "316.840", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt aber wird bis Mitte\u00a02020 gro\u00dfz\u00fcgig gef\u00f6rdert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "316.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "318.400", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "318.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "319.480", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gestatten Sie eine Zwischenfrage?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "319.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "320.080", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "320.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "321.280", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zur Begr\u00fcndung hei\u00dft es, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "321.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "325.120", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die angelaufenen Projekte ben\u00f6tigten eine l\u00e4ngere Laufzeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "325.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "327.640", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um komplett umgesetzt zu werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "327.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "328.240", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "328.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "329.320", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die AfD, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "329.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "330.160", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "k\u00f6nnen verstehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "330.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "335.440", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Unternehmer und Initiativen vor Ort dieses F\u00f6rderangebot gerne annehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "335.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "337.160", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sinnvoller w\u00e4re es aber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "337.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "340.000", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bundesweit alle Steuerzahler zu entlasten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "340.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "345.360", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem man solcherart Programme auslaufen l\u00e4sst."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "345.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "349.080", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gute Gesch\u00e4ftsideen m\u00fcssten sich dann aus eigener Kraft durchsetzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "349.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "353.360", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es einer sozialen Marktwirtschaft entspricht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "353.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "355.200", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das w\u00e4re ein Zukunftskonzept, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "355.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "357.240", 
   "id": "s000083", 
